<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>TEKNNUKU Studio — We Build Companies, Not Just Websites</title>
<meta name="description" content="Most agencies deliver a website. We deliver a revenue machine. TEKNNUKU Studio builds digital business systems that generate real income for serious founders and operators.">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Syne:wght@400;600;700;800&family=DM+Sans:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,500;0,600;1,400&family=DM+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>
/* ============================================
   RESET & ROOT
============================================ */
*, *::before, *::after { margin:0; padding:0; box-sizing:border-box; }

:root {
  --black:   #080808;
  --dark:    #0f0f0f;
  --panel:   #141414;
  --card:    #181818;
  --gold:    #C9A84C;
  --gold2:   #E2C16A;
  --cyan:    #00BCD4;
  --white:   #F2EDE4;
  --muted:   rgba(242,237,228,0.55);
  --dimmer:  rgba(242,237,228,0.35);
  --border:  rgba(201,168,76,0.18);
  --borderS: rgba(242,237,228,0.07);
  --r:       4px;
  --nav-h:   64px;
}

html { scroll-behavior:smooth; font-size:16px; }

body {
  font-family:'DM Sans', sans-serif;
  background:var(--black);
  color:var(--white);
  line-height:1.65;
  overflow-x:hidden;
  -webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;
}

img { max-width:100%; display:block; }
a { color:inherit; text-decoration:none; }
button { cursor:pointer; font-family:inherit; }
ul { list-style:none; }

/* ============================================
   TYPOGRAPHY
============================================ */
.t-eyebrow {
  font-family:'DM Mono', monospace;
  font-size:0.68rem;
  letter-spacing:0.18em;
  text-transform:uppercase;
  color:var(--gold);
  display:flex;
  align-items:center;
  gap:10px;
}
.t-eyebrow::before {
  content:'';
  width:18px; height:1px;
  background:var(--gold);
  display:inline-block;
  flex-shrink:0;
}

h1 { font-family:'Syne',sans-serif; font-weight:800; line-height:1.06; letter-spacing:-0.025em; }
h2 { font-family:'Syne',sans-serif; font-weight:800; line-height:1.1;  letter-spacing:-0.02em; }
h3 { font-family:'Syne',sans-serif; font-weight:700; line-height:1.2;  letter-spacing:-0.015em; }
h4 { font-family:'Syne',sans-serif; font-weight:700; line-height:1.3; }

p { font-size:1rem; color:var(--muted); line-height:1.75; }

/* ============================================
   LAYOUT
============================================ */
.wrap   { max-width:1160px; margin:0 auto; padding:0 clamp(20px,4vw,48px); width:100%; }
.wrap-s { max-width:860px;  margin:0 auto; padding:0 clamp(20px,4vw,48px); width:100%; }

section { padding:clamp(72px,10vw,120px) 0; }

.gold-rule { height:1px; background:linear-gradient(90deg,transparent,var(--gold) 40%,transparent); }

/* ============================================
   BUTTONS
============================================ */
.btn {
  display:inline-flex;
  align-items:center;
  gap:8px;
  padding:14px 28px;
  border-radius:var(--r);
  font-weight:600;
  font-size:0.88rem;
  letter-spacing:0.04em;
  text-transform:uppercase;
  transition:all .22s ease;
  border:none;
  white-space:nowrap;
  cursor:pointer;
}
.btn-gold    { background:var(--gold); color:#080808; }
.btn-gold:hover  { background:var(--gold2); transform:translateY(-2px); box-shadow:0 8px 24px rgba(201,168,76,.3); }
.btn-outline { background:transparent; color:var(--white); border:1px solid rgba(242,237,228,.25); }
.btn-outline:hover { border-color:var(--gold); color:var(--gold); }

/* ============================================
   HEADER / NAV
============================================ */
#site-header {
  position:fixed;
  top:0; left:0; right:0;
  z-index:999;
  height:var(--nav-h);
  background:rgba(8,8,8,.97);
  backdrop-filter:blur(14px);
  -webkit-backdrop-filter:blur(14px);
  border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);
  display:flex;
  align-items:center;
}

.nav-inner {
  display:flex;
  align-items:center;
  justify-content:space-between;
  gap:16px;
  width:100%;
  max-width:1160px;
  margin:0 auto;
  padding:0 clamp(20px,4vw,48px);
}

.logo-block { display:flex; flex-direction:column; line-height:1; flex-shrink:0; }
.logo-main {
  font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;
  font-weight:800;
  font-size:0.95rem;
  letter-spacing:0.06em;
  text-transform:uppercase;
  color:var(--white);
}
.logo-main em { color:var(--gold); font-style:normal; }
.logo-sub {
  font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;
  font-size:0.48rem;
  letter-spacing:0.14em;
  text-transform:uppercase;
  color:var(--dimmer);
  margin-top:3px;
}

.nav-links {
  display:flex;
  align-items:center;
  gap:24px;
}
.nav-links a {
  font-size:0.83rem;
  font-weight:500;
  color:var(--dimmer);
  transition:color .2s;
  white-space:nowrap;
}
.nav-links a:hover { color:var(--gold); }

.nav-right { display:flex; align-items:center; gap:10px; flex-shrink:0; }
.nav-btn-sm { padding:9px 16px; font-size:0.78rem; }

/* Hamburger */
.hamburger {
  display:none;
  flex-direction:column;
  justify-content:center;
  gap:5px;
  width:38px; height:38px;
  background:none;
  border:1px solid var(--borderS);
  border-radius:var(--r);
  padding:8px;
  transition:border-color .2s;
  flex-shrink:0;
}
.hamburger:hover { border-color:var(--gold); }
.hamburger span {
  display:block;
  height:1.5px;
  background:var(--white);
  border-radius:2px;
  transition:all .25s ease;
  transform-origin:center;
}
.hamburger.open span:nth-child(1) { transform:translateY(6.5px) rotate(45deg); }
.hamburger.open span:nth-child(2) { opacity:0; transform:scaleX(0); }
.hamburger.open span:nth-child(3) { transform:translateY(-6.5px) rotate(-45deg); }

/* Mobile drawer */
#mobile-nav {
  display:none;
  position:fixed;
  top:var(--nav-h);
  left:0; right:0;
  background:rgba(10,10,10,.99);
  backdrop-filter:blur(16px);
  -webkit-backdrop-filter:blur(16px);
  border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);
  z-index:998;
  padding:20px clamp(20px,4vw,48px) 28px;
  flex-direction:column;
  gap:0;
}
#mobile-nav.open { display:flex; }
#mobile-nav .mob-link {
  display:block;
  padding:14px 0;
  font-size:1rem;
  font-weight:500;
  color:var(--muted);
  border-bottom:1px solid var(--borderS);
  transition:color .2s, padding-left .2s;
}
#mobile-nav .mob-link:hover { color:var(--gold); padding-left:6px; }
#mobile-nav .mob-cta {
  margin-top:20px;
  display:block;
  text-align:center;
  padding:14px;
  border-radius:var(--r);
  background:var(--gold);
  color:#080808;
  font-weight:700;
  font-size:0.9rem;
  letter-spacing:0.04em;
  text-transform:uppercase;
}

/* ============================================
   HERO
============================================ */
.hero {
  min-height:100svh;
  display:flex;
  align-items:center;
  padding-top:var(--nav-h);
  position:relative;
  overflow:hidden;
}

.hero-bg {
  position:absolute; inset:0; pointer-events:none; z-index:0;
}
.hero-bg::before {
  content:''; position:absolute; inset:0;
  background:
    radial-gradient(ellipse 55% 55% at 8% 55%, rgba(201,168,76,.08) 0%, transparent 65%),
    radial-gradient(ellipse 40% 40% at 92% 25%, rgba(0,188,212,.07) 0%, transparent 65%);
}
.hero-bg::after {
  content:''; position:absolute; inset:0;
  background-image:
    linear-gradient(rgba(201,168,76,.04) 1px, transparent 1px),
    linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(201,168,76,.04) 1px, transparent 1px);
  background-size:52px 52px;
}

.hero-inner {
  position:relative; z-index:1;
  padding:clamp(48px,8vw,100px) 0;
}

.hero-tag { margin-bottom:28px; animation:fadeUp .6s ease both; }

.hero h1 {
  font-size:clamp(2.2rem, 6.5vw, 5.5rem);
  margin-bottom:28px;
  max-width:820px;
  animation:fadeUp .6s .1s ease both;
}
.hero h1 .g { color:var(--gold); }
.hero h1 .c { color:var(--cyan); }

.hero-lead {
  font-size:clamp(1rem,2.2vw,1.18rem);
  max-width:580px;
  margin-bottom:40px;
  color:var(--muted);
  line-height:1.8;
  animation:fadeUp .6s .2s ease both;
}

.hero-ctas {
  display:flex;
  flex-wrap:wrap;
  gap:12px;
  margin-bottom:clamp(40px,7vw,72px);
  animation:fadeUp .6s .3s ease both;
}

.sp-strip {
  display:flex;
  align-items:center;
  gap:10px;
  flex-wrap:wrap;
  animation:fadeUp .6s .4s ease both;
}
.sp-text {
  font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;
  font-size:0.65rem;
  letter-spacing:0.1em;
  color:var(--dimmer);
  text-transform:uppercase;
}
.sp-badges { display:flex; gap:8px; flex-wrap:wrap; }
.sp-badge {
  background:var(--panel);
  border:1px solid var(--borderS);
  padding:5px 12px;
  border-radius:2px;
  font-size:0.75rem;
  color:var(--muted);
}

.hero-stats {
  display:grid;
  grid-template-columns:repeat(4, 1fr);
  gap:1px;
  background:var(--borderS);
  border-top:1px solid var(--border);
  margin-top:clamp(36px,6vw,64px);
  animation:fadeUp .6s .5s ease both;
}
.stat-box {
  background:var(--black);
  padding:clamp(16px,2.5vw,26px) clamp(14px,2vw,24px);
}
.stat-box .n {
  font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;
  font-size:clamp(1.4rem,3vw,2.2rem);
  font-weight:800;
  color:var(--gold);
  display:block;
  line-height:1;
  margin-bottom:6px;
}
.stat-box .l {
  font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;
  font-size:0.6rem;
  letter-spacing:0.1em;
  text-transform:uppercase;
  color:var(--dimmer);
}

/* ============================================
   PROBLEM SECTION
============================================ */
.problem-section { background:var(--dark); }

.problem-grid {
  display:grid;
  grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;
  gap:2px;
  margin-top:clamp(32px,5vw,56px);
}

.prob-card {
  background:var(--panel);
  padding:clamp(24px,3.5vw,40px);
}
.prob-card .prob-icon { font-size:1.6rem; margin-bottom:14px; }
.prob-card h4 { font-size:1rem; color:var(--white); margin-bottom:10px; }
.prob-card p  { font-size:0.88rem; line-height:1.75; }

.prob-resolution {
  margin-top:2px;
  background:rgba(201,168,76,.07);
  border:1px solid var(--border);
  padding:clamp(26px,4vw,44px);
  display:flex;
  align-items:center;
  gap:clamp(20px,4vw,56px);
  flex-wrap:wrap;
}
.prob-resolution h3 { font-size:clamp(1.2rem,2.5vw,1.8rem); flex:1; min-width:200px; }
.prob-resolution .res-p { flex:1; min-width:200px; font-size:1rem; font-style:italic; color:var(--gold); font-weight:600; line-height:1.6; }
.prob-resolution .res-p small { display:block; color:var(--muted); font-weight:400; font-style:normal; font-size:0.88rem; margin-top:6px; }

/* ============================================
   IDENTITY
============================================ */
.identity-section { background:var(--black); }

.identity-split {
  display:grid;
  grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;
  gap:clamp(32px,6vw,80px);
  align-items:start;
  margin-top:clamp(32px,5vw,56px);
}

.id-left h2 { font-size:clamp(1.6rem,3.5vw,2.8rem); margin-bottom:20px; }
.id-left p  { font-size:0.95rem; margin-bottom:14px; }
.id-left .hl { color:var(--cyan); font-weight:600; }

.id-quote {
  background:rgba(201,168,76,.08);
  border-left:3px solid var(--gold);
  padding:20px 24px;
  margin-top:26px;
  border-radius:0 var(--r) var(--r) 0;
}
.id-quote p {
  font-size:1rem;
  font-style:italic;
  color:var(--gold);
  font-weight:600;
  line-height:1.6;
}

.id-right { display:flex; flex-direction:column; }

.id-card {
  padding:20px 0;
  border-bottom:1px solid var(--borderS);
}
.id-card:first-child { padding-top:0; }
.id-card:last-child  { border-bottom:none; }
.id-card .num {
  font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;
  font-size:0.6rem;
  color:var(--gold);
  letter-spacing:0.14em;
  text-transform:uppercase;
  margin-bottom:8px;
}
.id-card h4 { font-size:0.97rem; color:var(--white); margin-bottom:6px; }
.id-card p  { font-size:0.85rem; }

/* ============================================
   THREE ENGINES
============================================ */
.engines-section { background:var(--dark); }

.engines-grid {
  display:grid;
  grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);
  gap:2px;
  margin-top:clamp(32px,5vw,56px);
}

.eng-card {
  background:var(--panel);
  padding:clamp(24px,3.5vw,40px);
  position:relative;
  overflow:hidden;
  transition:background .25s;
}
.eng-card:hover { background:var(--card); }
.eng-card::before {
  content:''; position:absolute;
  top:0; left:0; right:0; height:2px;
}
.eng-gold::before  { background:var(--gold); }
.eng-cyan::before  { background:var(--cyan); }
.eng-white::before { background:rgba(242,237,228,.3); }

.eng-icon { font-size:1.8rem; margin-bottom:18px; display:block; }
.eng-card h3 { font-size:clamp(1.1rem,2vw,1.5rem); margin-bottom:12px; }
.eng-gold h3  { color:var(--gold); }
.eng-cyan h3  { color:var(--cyan); }
.eng-white h3 { color:var(--white); }
.eng-card p { font-size:0.88rem; line-height:1.75; margin-bottom:20px; }
.eng-goal {
  font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;
  font-size:0.62rem;
  letter-spacing:0.1em;
  text-transform:uppercase;
  padding-top:14px;
  border-top:1px solid var(--borderS);
}
.eng-gold .eng-goal  { color:var(--gold); }
.eng-cyan .eng-goal  { color:var(--cyan); }
.eng-white .eng-goal { color:var(--dimmer); }

/* ============================================
   SERVICES
============================================ */
.services-section { background:var(--black); }

.tier-nav {
  display:flex;
  gap:0;
  border-bottom:1px solid var(--borderS);
  margin:clamp(28px,5vw,52px) 0 0;
  overflow-x:auto;
  -webkit-overflow-scrolling:touch;
  scrollbar-width:none;
}
.tier-nav::-webkit-scrollbar { display:none; }

.tier-btn {
  background:none;
  border:none;
  border-bottom:2px solid transparent;
  padding:12px clamp(12px,2.5vw,24px);
  font-size:0.77rem;
  font-weight:600;
  letter-spacing:0.06em;
  text-transform:uppercase;
  color:var(--dimmer);
  font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;
  white-space:nowrap;
  margin-bottom:-1px;
  transition:all .2s;
}
.tier-btn:hover { color:var(--muted); }
.tier-btn.active { color:var(--gold); border-bottom-color:var(--gold); }

.tier-body { display:none; padding-top:clamp(28px,5vw,48px); }
.tier-body.active { display:block; }

.tier-head {
  display:grid;
  grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;
  gap:clamp(20px,4vw,56px);
  margin-bottom:clamp(28px,5vw,48px);
  align-items:start;
}
.tier-meta .badge {
  display:inline-block;
  padding:4px 12px;
  border-radius:2px;
  font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;
  font-size:0.6rem;
  letter-spacing:0.12em;
  text-transform:uppercase;
  margin-bottom:12px;
}
.t1 .badge { background:rgba(242,237,228,.06); color:var(--dimmer); }
.t2 .badge { background:rgba(201,168,76,.1); color:var(--gold); }
.t3 .badge { background:rgba(0,188,212,.1); color:var(--cyan); }
.ta .badge { background:rgba(242,237,228,.04); color:var(--dimmer); }

.tier-meta h3 { font-size:clamp(1.3rem,2.5vw,2rem); margin-bottom:12px; }
.tier-meta p { font-size:0.9rem; }

.tier-targets h5 {
  font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;
  font-size:0.6rem;
  color:var(--dimmer);
  letter-spacing:0.14em;
  text-transform:uppercase;
  margin-bottom:12px;
  font-weight:400;
}
.tags { display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:8px; }
.tag {
  background:var(--borderS);
  padding:5px 12px;
  border-radius:2px;
  font-size:0.77rem;
  color:var(--muted);
}

.pkg-grid {
  display:grid;
  grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(240px,1fr));
  gap:2px;
}

.pkg { background:var(--panel); padding:clamp(22px,3vw,36px); }
.pkg .pkg-name {
  font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;
  font-weight:700;
  font-size:1.05rem;
  color:var(--white);
  margin-bottom:8px;
}
.pkg .pkg-price {
  font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;
  font-size:0.8rem;
  color:var(--gold);
  display:block;
  margin-bottom:14px;
}
.pkg .pkg-pitch { font-size:0.86rem; margin-bottom:16px; }
.pkg-feat {
  list-style:none;
  border-top:1px solid var(--borderS);
  padding-top:12px;
}
.pkg-feat li {
  font-size:0.8rem;
  color:var(--muted);
  padding:5px 0 5px 16px;
  position:relative;
  border-bottom:1px solid rgba(242,237,228,.03);
}
.pkg-feat li:last-child { border-bottom:none; }
.pkg-feat li::before { content:'→'; position:absolute; left:0; color:var(--cyan); font-size:0.73rem; }

.addon-wrap {
  background:var(--panel);
  padding:clamp(24px,4vw,40px);
  margin-top:2px;
}
.addon-wrap h4 { font-size:1.05rem; color:var(--white); margin-bottom:24px; }
.addon-cols {
  display:grid;
  grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);
  gap:clamp(18px,3vw,36px);
}
.addon-col h5 {
  font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;
  font-size:0.6rem;
  color:var(--gold);
  letter-spacing:0.12em;
  text-transform:uppercase;
  font-weight:400;
  margin-bottom:10px;
}
.addon-col .ph { font-family:'DM Mono',monospace; font-size:0.7rem; color:var(--gold); margin-bottom:10px; }
.addon-col li { font-size:0.82rem; color:var(--muted); padding:4px 0; }

/* ============================================
   PROCESS
============================================ */
.process-section { background:var(--dark); }

.verb-rail {
  display:flex;
  border:1px solid var(--borderS);
  margin:clamp(24px,4vw,46px) 0;
  overflow-x:auto;
  -webkit-overflow-scrolling:touch;
  scrollbar-width:none;
}
.verb-rail::-webkit-scrollbar { display:none; }

.verb {
  flex:1;
  min-width:90px;
  padding:clamp(14px,2vw,24px) clamp(12px,1.8vw,20px);
  text-align:center;
  border-right:1px solid var(--borderS);
  display:flex;
  flex-direction:column;
  gap:5px;
}
.verb:last-child { border-right:none; }
.verb .vw {
  font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;
  font-weight:800;
  font-size:clamp(0.9rem,1.8vw,1.2rem);
  color:var(--gold);
}
.verb .vs {
  font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;
  font-size:0.55rem;
  letter-spacing:0.1em;
  text-transform:uppercase;
  color:var(--dimmer);
}

.step-grid {
  display:grid;
  grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);
  gap:2px;
}

.step { background:var(--panel); padding:clamp(22px,3vw,36px); }
.step .snum {
  font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;
  font-size:0.6rem;
  color:var(--gold);
  letter-spacing:0.14em;
  text-transform:uppercase;
  margin-bottom:14px;
  display:block;
}
.step h3 { font-size:clamp(0.97rem,1.6vw,1.15rem); color:var(--white); margin-bottom:10px; }
.step p  { font-size:0.86rem; }

.process-rule {
  margin-top:2px;
  background:rgba(201,168,76,.07);
  border:1px solid var(--border);
  padding:clamp(20px,3vw,32px) clamp(22px,4vw,42px);
  display:flex;
  align-items:center;
  gap:16px;
  flex-wrap:wrap;
}
.process-rule span { font-size:1.3rem; flex-shrink:0; }
.process-rule p {
  font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;
  font-size:clamp(0.92rem,1.8vw,1.05rem);
  font-weight:600;
  color:var(--gold);
}

/* ============================================
   VENTURES
============================================ */
.ventures-section { background:var(--black); }

.venture-grid {
  display:grid;
  grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(280px,1fr));
  gap:2px;
  margin-top:clamp(32px,5vw,56px);
}

.vc {
  background:var(--panel);
  padding:clamp(22px,3.5vw,36px);
  border-top:2px solid transparent;
  transition:border-color .25s, background .25s;
}
.vc:hover { border-top-color:var(--gold); background:var(--card); }

.vstatus {
  display:inline-block;
  font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;
  font-size:0.58rem;
  letter-spacing:0.12em;
  text-transform:uppercase;
  padding:4px 10px;
  border-radius:2px;
  margin-bottom:14px;
}
.s-cash     { background:rgba(0,188,212,.1); color:var(--cyan); }
.s-validate { background:rgba(201,168,76,.1); color:var(--gold); }
.s-build    { background:rgba(242,237,228,.05); color:var(--dimmer); }
.s-b2b      { background:rgba(180,120,255,.1); color:#b47aff; }

.vc h3 { font-size:clamp(1.2rem,2vw,1.5rem); color:var(--white); margin-bottom:8px; }
.vc .vrole { font-size:0.86rem; margin-bottom:18px; }

.vdetails { border-top:1px solid var(--borderS); padding-top:14px; }
.vdetails li {
  display:flex;
  justify-content:space-between;
  align-items:baseline;
  gap:12px;
  font-size:0.79rem;
  padding:5px 0;
  border-bottom:1px solid rgba(242,237,228,.03);
}
.vdetails li:last-child { border-bottom:none; }
.vdetails .dk {
  font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;
  font-size:0.58rem;
  color:var(--dimmer);
  letter-spacing:0.08em;
  text-transform:uppercase;
  flex-shrink:0;
}
.vdetails .dv { color:var(--muted); text-align:right; }
.vnote {
  margin-top:12px;
  font-size:0.78rem;
  font-weight:600;
  color:var(--cyan);
  padding-top:10px;
  border-top:1px solid var(--borderS);
}

/* ============================================
   POSITIONING
============================================ */
.pos-section { background:var(--dark); }

.pos-quote {
  background:var(--panel);
  border:1px solid var(--border);
  padding:clamp(32px,5vw,56px);
  margin-top:clamp(28px,5vw,46px);
  position:relative;
}
.pos-quote::before {
  content:'"'; position:absolute;
  top:14px; left:28px;
  font-size:4.5rem;
  font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;
  color:var(--gold);
  opacity:.12;
  line-height:1;
}
.pos-quote p {
  font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;
  font-size:clamp(1rem,2.5vw,1.65rem);
  font-weight:700;
  color:var(--white);
  line-height:1.5;
  position:relative; z-index:1;
}
.pos-quote p em { color:var(--gold); font-style:normal; }

.pos-rules {
  display:grid;
  grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;
  gap:2px;
  margin-top:2px;
}
.pr { background:var(--panel); padding:clamp(22px,3.5vw,36px); }
.pr .prl {
  font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;
  font-size:0.6rem;
  color:var(--dimmer);
  letter-spacing:0.14em;
  text-transform:uppercase;
  margin-bottom:12px;
}
.pr .no  { font-size:0.86rem; color:var(--dimmer); text-decoration:line-through; margin-bottom:4px; }
.pr .yes { font-family:'Syne',sans-serif; font-size:0.97rem; font-weight:700; color:var(--gold); margin-top:12px; }
.pr .desc { font-size:0.87rem; line-height:1.75; }

/* ============================================
   WHO WE SERVE
============================================ */
.who-section { background:var(--black); }

.who-grid {
  display:grid;
  grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(220px,1fr));
  gap:2px;
  margin-top:clamp(28px,5vw,48px);
}
.who-card {
  background:var(--panel);
  padding:clamp(18px,3vw,28px);
  border-left:2px solid var(--gold);
  transition:background .25s;
}
.who-card:hover { background:var(--card); }
.who-card p { font-size:0.9rem; color:var(--muted); }

.who-close {
  margin-top:clamp(28px,5vw,48px);
  background:rgba(201,168,76,.07);
  border:1px solid var(--border);
  padding:clamp(22px,4vw,36px);
  text-align:center;
}
.who-close p {
  font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;
  font-size:clamp(0.97rem,2vw,1.25rem);
  font-weight:700;
  color:var(--gold);
}

/* ============================================
   CTA
============================================ */
.cta-section {
  background:var(--dark);
  position:relative; overflow:hidden;
}
.cta-section::before {
  content:''; position:absolute; inset:0; pointer-events:none;
  background:
    radial-gradient(ellipse 50% 60% at 15% 50%, rgba(201,168,76,.08), transparent),
    radial-gradient(ellipse 40% 50% at 85% 50%, rgba(0,188,212,.06), transparent);
}
.cta-inner {
  position:relative; z-index:1;
  text-align:center;
  max-width:700px; margin:0 auto;
}
.cta-inner h2 { font-size:clamp(1.7rem,4.5vw,3.2rem); margin-bottom:18px; }
.cta-inner .cta-lead { font-size:clamp(0.95rem,1.8vw,1.1rem); margin-bottom:16px; line-height:1.75; }
.scarcity-note {
  display:inline-flex;
  align-items:center;
  gap:8px;
  background:rgba(242,237,228,.04);
  border:1px solid var(--borderS);
  padding:8px 16px;
  border-radius:2px;
  font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;
  font-size:0.63rem;
  letter-spacing:0.1em;
  text-transform:uppercase;
  color:var(--dimmer);
  margin-bottom:32px;
}
.scarcity-dot {
  width:6px; height:6px; border-radius:50%;
  background:#4caf50;
  animation:pulse 2s infinite;
  flex-shrink:0;
}
.cta-btns { display:flex; gap:12px; justify-content:center; flex-wrap:wrap; }

/* ============================================
   FOOTER
============================================ */
footer {
  background:var(--black);
  border-top:1px solid var(--border);
  padding:clamp(52px,8vw,86px) 0 clamp(24px,4vw,36px);
}

.footer-grid {
  display:grid;
  grid-template-columns:2fr 1fr 1fr 1fr;
  gap:clamp(28px,5vw,52px);
  margin-bottom:clamp(36px,6vw,56px);
}

.fb-name {
  font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;
  font-weight:800;
  font-size:1rem;
  letter-spacing:0.06em;
  text-transform:uppercase;
  margin-bottom:4px;
}
.fb-name em { color:var(--gold); font-style:normal; }
.fb-sub {
  font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;
  font-size:0.52rem;
  letter-spacing:0.14em;
  text-transform:uppercase;
  color:var(--dimmer);
  margin-bottom:16px;
}
.fb-desc { font-size:0.85rem; line-height:1.8; margin-bottom:14px; }
.fb-tagline {
  font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;
  font-size:0.64rem;
  letter-spacing:0.1em;
  text-transform:uppercase;
  color:var(--gold);
}

.fc h5 {
  font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;
  font-size:0.58rem;
  color:var(--gold);
  letter-spacing:0.15em;
  text-transform:uppercase;
  font-weight:400;
  margin-bottom:16px;
}
.fc a {
  display:block;
  font-size:0.83rem;
  color:var(--dimmer);
  padding:5px 0;
  transition:color .2s, padding-left .2s;
}
.fc a:hover { color:var(--gold); padding-left:4px; }

.footer-bottom {
  border-top:1px solid var(--borderS);
  padding-top:clamp(20px,3vw,28px);
  display:flex;
  justify-content:space-between;
  align-items:center;
  flex-wrap:wrap;
  gap:10px;
}
.footer-bottom p {
  font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;
  font-size:0.6rem;
  letter-spacing:0.07em;
  color:rgba(242,237,228,.28);
}

/* ============================================
   ANIMATIONS
============================================ */
@keyframes fadeUp {
  from { opacity:0; transform:translateY(20px); }
  to   { opacity:1; transform:translateY(0); }
}
@keyframes pulse {
  0%,100% { box-shadow:0 0 0 0 rgba(76,175,80,.4); }
  50%      { box-shadow:0 0 0 5px rgba(76,175,80,0); }
}

/* ============================================
   RESPONSIVE — TABLET ≤900px
============================================ */
@media (max-width:900px) {
  .nav-links { display:none; }
  .nav-right .btn-outline { display:none; }
  .hamburger { display:flex; }

  .identity-split { grid-template-columns:1fr; }
  .engines-grid   { grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; }
  .step-grid      { grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; }
  .problem-grid   { grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; }
  .tier-head      { grid-template-columns:1fr; gap:24px; }
  .pos-rules      { grid-template-columns:1fr; }
  .footer-grid    { grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; }
  .addon-cols     { grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; }
  .hero-stats     { grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr); }
}

/* ============================================
   RESPONSIVE — MOBILE ≤600px
============================================ */
@media (max-width:600px) {
  :root { --nav-h:58px; }

  .hero h1 { font-size:clamp(1.9rem,8.5vw,2.8rem); }
  .hero-ctas { flex-direction:column; }
  .hero-ctas .btn { width:100%; justify-content:center; }
  .hero-stats { grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; }

  .engines-grid { grid-template-columns:1fr; }
  .step-grid    { grid-template-columns:1fr; }
  .problem-grid { grid-template-columns:1fr; }
  .who-grid     { grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; }
  .footer-grid  { grid-template-columns:1fr; gap:28px; }
  .addon-cols   { grid-template-columns:1fr; }

  .prob-resolution { flex-direction:column; }
  .process-rule    { flex-direction:column; }
  .cta-btns { flex-direction:column; }
  .cta-btns .btn { width:100%; justify-content:center; }
  .footer-bottom { flex-direction:column; gap:6px; text-align:center; }
}

@media (max-width:380px) {
  .who-grid { grid-template-columns:1fr; }
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- ============================================
     HEADER
============================================ -->
<header id="site-header">
  <div class="nav-inner">

    <a href="#" class="logo-block">
      <span class="logo-main">TEKNNUKU <em>STUDIO</em></span>
      <span class="logo-sub">Venture Factory · Revenue Infrastructure</span>
    </a>

    <nav class="nav-links" aria-label="Main navigation">
      <a href="#engines">What We Do</a>
      <a href="#services">Services</a>
      <a href="#ventures">Ventures</a>
      <a href="#process">Process</a>
      <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
    </nav>

    <div class="nav-right">
      <a href="https://calendly.com/teknnuku" class="btn btn-outline nav-btn-sm">Book a Call</a>
      <a href="/pagebuilder.html" class="btn btn-gold nav-btn-sm">Start Project</a>
      <button class="hamburger" id="hamburger" aria-label="Toggle navigation" aria-expanded="false">
        <span></span><span></span><span></span>
      </button>
    </div>

  </div>
</header>

<!-- Mobile Drawer -->
<nav id="mobile-nav" aria-label="Mobile navigation">
  <a href="#engines"  class="mob-link">What We Do</a>
  <a href="#services" class="mob-link">Services &amp; Pricing</a>
  <a href="#ventures" class="mob-link">Active Ventures</a>
  <a href="#process"  class="mob-link">Our Process</a>
  <a href="#contact"  class="mob-link">Contact</a>
  <a href="/pagebuilder.html" class="mob-cta">Start a Project →</a>
</nav>

<!-- ============================================
     HERO
============================================ -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-bg" aria-hidden="true"></div>
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="hero-inner">

      <div class="t-eyebrow hero-tag">TEKNNUKU Studio — Venture Factory</div>

      <h1>
        Most agencies give you a website.<br>
        <span class="g">We give you</span> <span class="c">a revenue machine.</span>
      </h1>

      <p class="hero-lead">
        While your competitors pay for pretty pages that don't convert, 
        TEKNNUKU Studio builds digital systems engineered to generate income 
        from day one. Serious founders only.
      </p>

      <div class="hero-ctas">
        <a href="/pagebuilder.html" class="btn btn-gold">Start a Project →</a>
        <a href="#engines" class="btn btn-outline">See How We Build</a>
      </div>

      <div class="sp-strip">
        <span class="sp-text">Trusted by</span>
        <div class="sp-badges">
          <span class="sp-badge">Founders</span>
          <span class="sp-badge">Operators</span>
          <span class="sp-badge">Startups</span>
          <span class="sp-badge">Enterprise</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="hero-stats">
        <div class="stat-box"><span class="n">5</span><span class="l">Live Ventures</span></div>
        <div class="stat-box"><span class="n">3</span><span class="l">Service Tiers</span></div>
        <div class="stat-box"><span class="n">₦50M+</span><span class="l">Build Capacity</span></div>
        <div class="stat-box"><span class="n">1</span><span class="l">Ecosystem</span></div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="gold-rule"></div>

<!-- ============================================
     PROBLEM — Pain → Agitate → Solve
============================================ -->
<section class="problem-section">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="t-eyebrow">The Real Problem</div>
    <h2 style="font-size:clamp(1.7rem,4vw,2.8rem);margin-top:14px;max-width:680px;">
      You don't have a traffic problem.<br>You have a <span style="color:var(--gold)">conversion problem.</span>
    </h2>

    <div class="problem-grid">
      <div class="prob-card">
        <div class="prob-icon">😤</div>
        <h4>You paid for a website. It sits there doing nothing.</h4>
        <p>Thousands spent on design. Zero in return. The agency delivered what they promised — but nobody promised revenue.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="prob-card">
        <div class="prob-icon">🔁</div>
        <h4>You're trapped in the "build, wait, hope" cycle.</h4>
        <p>Launch. Crickets. Tweak. Crickets. Most founders repeat this for years before realising the platform itself was broken from the start.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="prob-card">
        <div class="prob-icon">⚙️</div>
        <h4>Your infrastructure is built for looks — not growth.</h4>
        <p>A beautiful website that doesn't convert is an expensive billboard in a desert. Impressive. Useless.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="prob-card">
        <div class="prob-icon">📉</div>
        <h4>Every month without a system is money left behind.</h4>
        <p>While you figure it out, your market is moving. Every week without a working funnel is compounding lost revenue.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="prob-resolution">
      <h3>We answer one question before anything else:</h3>
      <div>
        <p class="res-p">"How does this platform make money?"
          <small>If we can't answer that clearly — we don't build it. That one question saves founders years and millions.</small>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="gold-rule"></div>

<!-- ============================================
     IDENTITY
============================================ -->
<section class="identity-section" id="engines">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="t-eyebrow">What We Are</div>
    <div class="identity-split">

      <div class="id-left">
        <h2>The venture factory behind the TEKNNUKU ecosystem</h2>
        <p>TEKNNUKU Studio is not a web agency. It is the <span class="hl">venture-building arm</span> of the TEKNNUKU ecosystem — the unit that systematically creates, tests, and launches revenue-generating businesses.</p>
        <p>Inside every serious empire, there is a builder. The HoldCo allocates capital. The Studio turns it into companies. OpCos run what survives. We are the Studio — and we extend that same capability to our clients.</p>
        <p>We don't just advise founders. We are the founder and the builder — and when we take your project on, we treat it exactly as we treat our own.</p>
        <div class="id-quote">
          <p>"A factory that builds companies — not just ideas."</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="id-right">
        <div class="id-card">
          <div class="num">// 01 Design</div>
          <h4>Revenue architecture before a single pixel is drawn</h4>
          <p>We define the business model, the customer journey, and the monetisation structure before design begins. Strategy is never an afterthought here.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="id-card">
          <div class="num">// 02 Validate</div>
          <h4>Real users. Real payments. Or we kill it.</h4>
          <p>We don't rely on opinions or gut feeling. We look for one thing: will someone actually pay? No payment signal means no further investment — simple as that.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="id-card">
          <div class="num">// 03 Incubate</div>
          <h4>Winners get fuel. Losers get cut — fast.</h4>
          <p>This is how venture studios outperform agencies and solo founders. Ruthless resource allocation protects your capital and focuses energy where it actually compounds.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="id-card">
          <div class="num">// 04 Spin-Out</div>
          <h4>The product becomes its own company</h4>
          <p>When a product reaches product-market fit, it becomes a standalone operating company — its own team, its own capital, and aggressive scale from there.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="gold-rule"></div>

<!-- ============================================
     THREE ENGINES
============================================ -->
<section class="engines-section">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="t-eyebrow">Studio Architecture</div>
    <h2 style="font-size:clamp(1.7rem,4vw,2.8rem);margin-top:14px;max-width:620px;">Three machines running under one roof</h2>
    <p style="margin-top:12px;max-width:560px;font-size:0.95rem;">Each engine funds the next. Cash from services builds client platforms. Client platforms seed internal ventures. Internal ventures become the empire.</p>

    <div class="engines-grid">
      <div class="eng-card eng-gold">
        <span class="eng-icon">🪙</span>
        <h3>Engine 1 — Studio Services</h3>
        <p>Volume-driven work for growing businesses — brand systems, landing pages, and business setups. Priced for accessibility, engineered for results. This is the front door that funds the factory.</p>
        <div class="eng-goal">Purpose: Cash flow + client pipeline</div>
      </div>
      <div class="eng-card eng-cyan">
        <span class="eng-icon">🏗️</span>
        <h3>Engine 2 — Custom Digital Systems</h3>
        <p>High-ticket B2B platform engineering. Custom SaaS, enterprise marketplaces, automation infrastructure, and white-label systems for companies that operate at scale. This is where the Studio becomes genuinely dangerous.</p>
        <div class="eng-goal">Purpose: Premium revenue + market authority</div>
      </div>
      <div class="eng-card eng-white">
        <span class="eng-icon">🚀</span>
        <h3>Engine 3 — Internal Venture Factory</h3>
        <p>Jobletters, TEK1SECURITY, PowerPlus, and beyond. We build these with the same systems we use for clients — validate fast, kill early, scale only what wins. Equity is the long game.</p>
        <div class="eng-goal">Purpose: Long-term asymmetric upside</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="gold-rule"></div>

<!-- ============================================
     SERVICES
============================================ -->
<section class="services-section" id="services">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="t-eyebrow">Service Menu</div>
    <h2 style="font-size:clamp(1.7rem,4vw,2.8rem);margin-top:14px;">Choose your entry point</h2>
    <p style="margin-top:12px;max-width:560px;font-size:0.92rem;">Most clients start at Tier 1. The serious ones graduate to Tier 3. Every tier is held to the same standard — because every client deserves infrastructure that works.</p>

    <div class="tier-nav" role="tablist">
      <button class="tier-btn active" data-tier="t1" role="tab" aria-selected="true">🟢 Tier 1 — Starter</button>
      <button class="tier-btn" data-tier="t2" role="tab">🟡 Tier 2 — Growth</button>
      <button class="tier-btn" data-tier="t3" role="tab">🔴 Tier 3 — Platforms</button>
      <button class="tier-btn" data-tier="ta" role="tab">➕ Add-Ons</button>
    </div>

    <!-- TIER 1 -->
    <div class="tier-body t1 active" id="t1" role="tabpanel">
      <div class="tier-head">
        <div class="tier-meta">
          <span class="badge">Tier 1 · Starter Services</span>
          <h3>Stop looking like a side hustle. Start winning trust instantly.</h3>
          <p>The first thing your customers do is search for you. What they find in the next 8 seconds determines whether they buy or bounce. These packages ensure what they see builds credibility — not doubt.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="tier-targets">
          <h5>This Tier is For</h5>
          <div class="tags">
            <span class="tag">Instagram Vendors</span>
            <span class="tag">TikTok Sellers</span>
            <span class="tag">Facebook Business</span>
            <span class="tag">Freelancers</span>
            <span class="tag">Side Hustlers</span>
            <span class="tag">New Operators</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="pkg-grid">
        <div class="pkg">
          <div class="pkg-name">Brand Starter Kit</div>
          <span class="pkg-price">₦25,000 – ₦75,000</span>
          <p class="pkg-pitch">People buy from businesses they trust. This kit gives you the visual credibility to earn that trust immediately — before you say a single word.</p>
          <ul class="pkg-feat">
            <li>Logo design</li>
            <li>Brand colours + font system</li>
            <li>Simple brand guide</li>
            <li>Social profile optimisation</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="pkg">
          <div class="pkg-name">Brand Authority Kit</div>
          <span class="pkg-price">₦80,000 – ₦200,000</span>
          <p class="pkg-pitch">When you look like the authority in your niche, people stop comparing prices. This kit positions you as the obvious choice — not just another option competing on cost.</p>
          <ul class="pkg-feat">
            <li>Full brand blueprint</li>
            <li>Brand voice guide</li>
            <li>Instagram page setup</li>
            <li>Highlight covers</li>
            <li>Content templates</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="pkg">
          <div class="pkg-name">Business Launch Page</div>
          <span class="pkg-price">₦120,000 – ₦350,000</span>
          <p class="pkg-pitch">Your customers are searching for what you sell right now. Own a professional home on the internet that captures them and converts them — instead of sending them to a competitor.</p>
          <ul class="pkg-feat">
            <li>One-page website or landing page</li>
            <li>Mobile-first design</li>
            <li>WhatsApp integration</li>
            <li>Contact form + lead capture</li>
            <li>Basic SEO setup</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- TIER 2 -->
    <div class="tier-body t2" id="t2" role="tabpanel">
      <div class="tier-head">
        <div class="tier-meta">
          <span class="badge">Tier 2 · Growth Systems</span>
          <h3>Turn your business into a machine that runs without you chasing every sale.</h3>
          <p>When your digital infrastructure works correctly, customers find you, trust you, book you, and pay you — while you focus on delivery. These systems make that your default reality.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="tier-targets">
          <h5>This Tier is For</h5>
          <div class="tags">
            <span class="tag">Established SMEs</span>
            <span class="tag">Logistics Companies</span>
            <span class="tag">Agencies</span>
