<!-- ============================================
     PROCESS
============================================ -->
<section class="process-section" id="process">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="t-eyebrow">How We Work</div>
    <h2 style="font-size:clamp(1.7rem,4vw,2.8rem);margin-top:14px;">Five verbs. Zero wasted time.</h2>
    <p style="margin-top:12px;max-width:540px;font-size:0.92rem;">Most agencies iterate endlessly and bill by the hour. We move by outcome. Every project follows the same proven sequence — because it works every time.</p>

    <div class="verb-rail">
      <div class="verb"><span class="vw">Design</span><span class="vs">Architecture first</span></div>
      <div class="verb"><span class="vw">Build</span><span class="vs">Fast MVPs</span></div>
      <div class="verb"><span class="vw">Validate</span><span class="vs">Real payments</span></div>
      <div class="verb"><span class="vw">Incubate</span><span class="vs">Or kill</span></div>
      <div class="verb"><span class="vw">De-risk</span><span class="vs">Scale winners</span></div>
    </div>

    <div class="step-grid">
      <div class="step">
        <span class="snum">// Step 01</span>
        <h3>Strategy &amp; Architecture</h3>
        <p>Before we open a design file, we answer the question every platform must answer: how does this make money? Revenue model, audience, and structure come first. Always.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <span class="snum">// Step 02</span>
        <h3>Rapid MVP Creation</h3>
        <p>We build the simplest version that can generate a real market signal. Not a prototype. Not a mockup. A working product in the hands of real potential customers — fast.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <span class="snum">// Step 03</span>
        <h3>Paid Market Validation</h3>
        <p>We don't celebrate activity — we celebrate payment. Real users paying real money. No payment signal means we pivot or kill. This saves years and protects capital.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <span class="snum">// Step 04</span>
        <h3>Spin-Out or Scale</h3>
        <p>Winners reach product-market fit, get their own company, their own team, and are scaled aggressively. Losers are shut down before they drain the system. Both outcomes are victories.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="process-rule">
      <span>⚙️</span>
      <p>Every project is built as permanent infrastructure — not a one-time deliverable. We build it once. We build it right. It compounds from there.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="gold-rule"></div>

